                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-12-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 13, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Root informs Mr. Rockhill that he has agreed with the Chinese minister to
                    reduce the Lienchou final indemnity to $25,000 gold, and authorizes him to
                    close, with this modification, the agreement set forth in his No. 381.)</p>
            </div>
